<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.1.10">
<l>tottār pūṅkuḻal kaṉṉi yoruttiyaic cōlait taṭamkoṇṭu pukku</l>
<l>muttār koṅkai puṇarntirā nāḻikai mūvēḻu ceṉṟapiṉ vantāy</l>
<l>ottārk kottaṉa pēcuva ruṉṉai yurappavē nāṉoṉṟum māṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>attā vuṉṉai yaṟintukoṇ ṭēṉuṉak kañcuva ṉammam taravē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Taking one maiden, her curls full of blossom clusters,</l>
<l rend="indent">into the huge grove,</l>
<l>and embracing her pearl laden breasts [all] night,</l>
<l rend="indent">you returned only after 21 nāḻikais.</l>
<l>They will say what is appropriate for those who are appropriate,</l>
<l rend="indent">[but] I am not able to frighten you at all, Lord!</l>
<l>I have come to know you,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] I am afraid to give you [my] breast milk.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
